query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from tag_question AS tq
inner join question AS q
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 0 AND q.score <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('bar-chart',
'converter',
'firemonkey',
'gradient',
'grouping',
'gruntjs',
'inversion-of-control',
'keras',
'marshalling',
'message-queue',
'plist',
'sql-injection',
'submit',
'trigonometry',
'user-input');
